.panel.panel-warning
  .panel-heading
    %h1.panel-title You account needs to be activated
  .panel-body.lead
    %p
      If you have just signed up for a new account you should receive an email shortly.

    %p
      You will need to follow the instructions in the activation email before you can sign into other GINA services with this account.

.panel.panel-info
  .panel-heading
    %h1.panel-title Problems activating our account?
  .panel-body
    %h3 I haven't received an email asking to activate my account
    %p.lead Check your spam filter or folder and make sure that support@gina.alaska.edu is allowed to send you email.

    %h3 I need to change my emails address
    %p.lead You register with #{current_user.email}, #{link_to 'Click here to change your settings', users_path}

    %h3 I'm still having trouble
    %p.lead If you're still having problems activating your account please send an email to #{mail_to 'support@gina.alaska.edu', 'support@gina.alaska.edu', target: :_blank}
